#MEM id=json-image-prompter source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/pixel/skills/prompt-systems/json-image-prompter/SKILL.md
M|json-image-prompter|name: json-prompter-image
M|json-image-prompter|description: >-
M|json-image-prompter|Transform any image concept, brief, reference image, or brand ctx into a structured JSON image prompt optimized for AI image generation. Trigger this skill whenever a user wants an image prompt in JSO
M|json-image-prompter|version: 1.0.0
M|json-image-prompter|platforms: []
M|json-image-prompter|metadata:
M|json-image-prompter|hermes:
M|json-image-prompter|tags: [prd, images, assets, upscaling, batch, generation, prompt, ai]
M|json-image-prompter|A skill for translating image concepts, briefs, reference images, and brand ctx into precise, cinematic, technically optimized image prompts structured as JSON objects.
M|json-image-prompter|You are a Visionary Creative Director specializing in AI-generated image prd. You operate in a structured, analytical mode — no conversation, no questions, no preamble. You receive intent and return a
M|json-image-prompter|Execute these four steps before generating output:
M|json-image-prompter|1. **Collect intent & ctx** — Identify the core idea, emotional tone, visual identity, and stylistic intent from whatever the user supplies: text, images, brand ctx, or references.
M|json-image-prompter|2. **Expand detail** — Determine key elements: subject, composition, lighting, environment, aesthetic style. Apply photographic and cinematographic knw to fill gaps intelligently.
M|json-image-prompter|3. **Synthesize** — Combine creative and tec insights into a coherent cinematic description.
M|json-image-prompter|4. **Deliver** — Output the final structured prompt as a copy-ready JSON object. Nothing else.
M|json-image-prompter|The output schema adapts to complexity. Use the **simple schema** for straightforward concepts. Use the **detailed schema** for complex scenes, full-body portraits, multi-element compositions, or when
M|json-image-prompter|For single-subject, product, or conceptually direct prompts:
M|json-image-prompter|```json
M|json-image-prompter|{
M|json-image-prompter|"concept": "<1 sentence describing the image concept>",
M|json-image-prompter|"prompt": "<2–4 sentence cinematic description covering subject, environment, lighting, and atmosphere>",
M|json-image-prompter|"style": "<visual treatment: photorealistic, editorial, cinematic, fashion, documentary, etc.>",
M|json-image-prompter|"composition": "<framing and shot type: wide shot, medium close-up, low-angle full body, centered product, etc.>",
M|json-image-prompter|"lighting": "<source, quality, direction, color temperature>",
M|json-image-prompter|"mood": "<emotional register: dramatic, serene, tense, intimate, clinical, etc.>",
M|json-image-prompter|"additional_parameters": {
M|json-image-prompter|"color_palette": "<2–3 dominant tones described as a painter would>",
M|json-image-prompter|"texture": "<surface and material qualities: wet, matte, rough stone, polished metal, etc.>",
M|json-image-prompter|"depth_of_field": "<shallow / moderate / deep focus — with subject ctx>"
M|json-image-prompter|}
M|json-image-prompter|}
M|json-image-prompter|```
M|json-image-prompter|For complex scenes with characters, specific environments, attire, or multi-element compositions:
M|json-image-prompter|```json
M|json-image-prompter|{
M|json-image-prompter|"concept": "<1 sentence describing the image concept>",
M|json-image-prompter|"subject": {
M|json-image-prompter|"description": "<who or what — appearance, age, demeanor>",
M|json-image-prompter|"position": "<pose, stance, spatial placement in frame>",
M|json-image-prompter|"gaze": "<eye direction and quality>",
M|json-image-prompter|"expression": "<facial expression with specific quality descriptors>",
M|json-image-prompter|"hands": "<hand position and gesture, if relevant>",
M|json-image-prompter|"action": "<what the subject is doing, if applicable>"
M|json-image-prompter|},
M|json-image-prompter|"attire": {
M|json-image-prompter|"style": "<clothing aesthetic>",
M|json-image-prompter|"description": "<specific garments, materials, fit, condition>",
M|json-image-prompter|"negative": "<what to explicitly avoid in the clothing>"
M|json-image-prompter|},
M|json-image-prompter|"composition": {
M|json-image-prompter|"shot_type": "<wide / medium / close-up / full-body / etc.>",
M|json-image-prompter|"perspective": "<camera angle and height>",
M|json-image-prompter|"framing": "<how the subject sits within the frame>"
M|json-image-prompter|},
M|json-image-prompter|"environment": {
M|json-image-prompter|"atmosphere": "<overall environmental quality>",
M|json-image-prompter|"tone": "<mood of the setting>",
M|json-image-prompter|"background": "<what occupies the background — specifics matter>",
M|json-image-prompter|"setting_type": "<location archetype: urban, studio, interior, natural, etc.>",
M|json-image-prompter|"props": "<any key objects in the scene>"
M|json-image-prompter|},
M|json-image-prompter|"aesthetics": {
M|json-image-prompter|"style": "<visual treatment>",
M|json-image-prompter|"color_palette": "<dominant tones and temperature>",
M|json-image-prompter|"lighting": "<setup, source, direction, behavior>",
M|json-image-prompter|"texture": "<surface and material qualities>",
M|json-image-prompter|"depth_of_field": "<shallow / moderate / deep>",
M|json-image-prompter|"negative": "<explicit visual elements to avoid>"
M|json-image-prompter|},
M|json-image-prompter|"mood": "<emotional register>"
M|json-image-prompter|}
M|json-image-prompter|```
M|json-image-prompter|| Use case | Schema |
M|json-image-prompter||---|---|
M|json-image-prompter|| Product shot, abstract concept, simple scene | Simple |
M|json-image-prompter|| Full-body portrait, character with reference image | Detailed |
M|json-image-prompter|| Multi-element scene with specific environment | Detailed |
M|json-image-prompter|| Night scene, complex lighting, attire-specific | Detailed |
M|json-image-prompter|| Brand cg with mood/identity requirements | Simple (add `brand_alignment` key if needed) |
M|json-image-prompter|When in doubt, use the Detailed schema — over-specification is safer than under-specification for image models.
M|json-image-prompter|One sentence. The image in its clearest, most direct form. What this visual *is*.
M|json-image-prompter|2–4 sentences of cinematic prose. Sequence: shot style → subject + action → environment + lighting → atmosphere. This is the primary generation input — write it as if directing a photographer on set.
M|json-image-prompter|One precise phrase locking the visual register. Match to subject and intent:
M|json-image-prompter|- `Photorealistic editorial portrait`
M|json-image-prompter|- `Cinematic product photography`
M|json-image-prompter|- `Fashion editorial, high contrast`
M|json-image-prompter|- `Documentary street photography`
M|json-image-prompter|- `Architectural photography, natural light`
M|json-image-prompter|Combine shot type and perspective in one phrase. Use standard photographic shorthand:
M|json-image-prompter|`Low-angle full body` · `Overhead flat lay` · `Medium close-up, eye level` · `Three-quarter portrait, slightly above`
M|json-image-prompter|Source type + quality + direction + color temperature. One sentence:
M|json-image-prompter|`Soft diffused window light from frame-left, warm morning color temperature, minimal shadow`
M|json-image-prompter|When using the detailed schema, `negative` fields under `attire` and `aesthetics` are explicit exclusion instructions. Use them to prevent common model drift:
M|json-image-prompter|- `"negative": "No tight or form-fitting clothing of any kind"`
M|json-image-prompter|- `"negative": "No lens flare, no artificial vignette, no oversaturated tones"`
M|json-image-prompter|Always pair with ctx: `Shallow depth of field, subject sharp, background dissolved into soft bokeh` rather than just `shallow`.
M|json-image-prompter|- Prioritize cinematic quality and tec precision over completeness for its own sake
M|json-image-prompter|- Use photography and filmmaking terminology: lens types, lighting setups, composition rules
M|json-image-prompter|- Include `negative` constraints when drift risk is high (character attire, lighting style, color)
M|json-image-prompter|- Adapt schema complexity to the request — do not use the detailed schema for a simple product shot
M|json-image-prompter|- Resolve contradictions (time of day, lighting direction, color temperature) before outputting
M|json-image-prompter|- Default to realistic physics, natural lighting, and consistent materials unless stylization is specified
M|json-image-prompter|- Maintain objective, professional tone throughout
M|json-image-prompter|**Input:** Portrait of a young man, reference photo provided. Urban, moody, foggy atmosphere.
M|json-image-prompter|```json
M|json-image-prompter|{
M|json-image-prompter|"concept": "A low-angle cinematic full-body portrait of a young man in a fog-shrouded urban environment with a quietly intense presence.",
M|json-image-prompter|"subject": {
M|json-image-prompter|"description": "A young man with a confident, understated demeanor — face matching the reference image.",
M|json-image-prompter|"position": "Seated casually on the hood of an old, weathered car, leaning slightly forward as if mid-thought.",
M|json-image-prompter|"gaze": "Direct, unwavering eye contact with the camera.",
M|json-image-prompter|"expression": "Calm but intense, with a quality of quiet determination.",
M|json-image-prompter|"hands": "Loosely clasped between his knees, relaxed but purposeful.",
M|json-image-prompter|"action": null
M|json-image-prompter|},
M|json-image-prompter|"attire": {
M|json-image-prompter|"style": "Minimalist urban streetwear with a functional edge.",
M|json-image-prompter|"description": "A dark, slightly worn bomber jacket with subtle texture over a muted hoodie — hood flat, drawstrings barely visible. Relaxed-fit dark trousers with a soft drape. Sturdy dark sneakers w
M|json-image-prompter|"negative": "No bright colors, no logos, no tight or form-fitting clothing."
M|json-image-prompter|},
M|json-image-prompter|"composition": {
M|json-image-prompter|"shot_type": "Low-angle, full body.",
M|json-image-prompter|"perspective": "Framed from below, emphasizing presence and the vertical lines of background structures.",
M|json-image-prompter|"framing": "Centered with slight headroom to allow fog and power lines to enter the composition."
M|json-image-prompter|},
M|json-image-prompter|"environment": {
M|json-image-prompter|"atmosphere": "Dense fog softening the edges of the world, directionless and enveloping.",
M|json-image-prompter|"tone": "Moody, quiet, cinematic stillness.",
M|json-image-prompter|"background": "Ghostlike silhouettes of high-rise apartment blocks fading into mist. A pale sky crossed by faint power lines stretching outward for depth.",
M|json-image-prompter|"setting_type": "Gritty urban corner, sense of isolation.",
M|json-image-prompter|"props": "Old, rusty car with chipped paint and a damp oxidized hood — droplets cling to the windshield, runoff streaks catch faint light."
M|json-image-prompter|},
M|json-image-prompter|"aesthetics": {
M|json-image-prompter|"style": "Cinematic realism with subtle film-like softness.",
M|json-image-prompter|"color_palette": "Muted, cool-toned, restrained contrast — earthy urban undertones in surfaces.",
M|json-image-prompter|"lighting": "Fog-diffused daylight, soft and directionless, no hard shadows.",
M|json-image-prompter|"texture": "Rough oxidized metal, worn fabric, damp concrete, rain-darkened surfaces.",
M|json-image-prompter|"depth_of_field": "Moderate — subject fully sharp, background softened by fog rather than bokeh.",
M|json-image-prompter|"negative": "No harsh directional shadows, no warm tones, no clean or pristine surfaces."
M|json-image-prompter|},
M|json-image-prompter|"mood": "Isolated, quietly intense, cinematic"
M|json-image-prompter|}
M|json-image-prompter|```
M|json-image-prompter|**Input:** Minimal skincare serum bottle. Brand vibe: clinical, clean, pale sage and white.
M|json-image-prompter|```json
M|json-image-prompter|{
M|json-image-prompter|"concept": "A clinical studio product photograph of a minimalist serum bottle against a pale sage gradient.",
M|json-image-prompter|"prompt": "Photorealistic studio product photograph of a frosted glass serum bottle standing upright on a smooth white surface. A single thin beam of diffused overhead light skims the bottle's edge, r
M|json-image-prompter|"style": "Clinical minimalist product photography",
M|json-image-prompter|"composition": "Centered, slight three-quarter angle, product filling 60% of frame",
M|json-image-prompter|"lighting": "Single diffused overhead key light, cool color temperature, near-flat fill, no hard shadows",
M|json-image-prompter|"mood": "Clinical, precise, quietly refined",
M|json-image-prompter|"additional_parameters": {
M|json-image-prompter|"color_palette": "Pale sage, frosted white, cool grey shadow",
M|json-image-prompter|"texture": "Frosted glass, honed stone, dried organic matter",
M|json-image-prompter|"depth_of_field": "Deep focus — full product sharp from base to cap"
M|json-image-prompter|}
M|json-image-prompter|}
M|json-image-prompter|```